   <abstract>This briefing book includes a series of fact sheets concerning child care, early education, and school-age care, as well as information on major child care, early education, and school-age policies and programs. The fact sheets make a compelling case for investing in efforts to help children and families overcome the myriad child care, early education, and school-age challenges they face each day so they can get the quality early learning and after-school experiences they need to succeed.</abstract>
